OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,FThe mother of a 17-year-old boy, who
OL,7,Fsaid she had her heart 'ripped out'
OL,8,Fafter her son died in a car accident,
OL,9,Fhas urged teenagers to stay safe
OL,10,Fbehind the wheel at an event at a
OL,11,FWrexham college.
OL,13,FCrystal Owen lost her son Harvey Owen
OL,14,Fin November 2023 after the car he and
OL,15,Fthree other teenage boys were
OL,16,Ftravelling in crashed into a flooded
OL,17,Fditch in Gwynedd whilst returning from
OL,18,Fa camping trip.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
