CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777551071
OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,FHarvey and his friends Hugo Morris,
OL,7,FWilf Fitchett and Jevon Hirst had been
OL,8,Fvisiting Eryri National Park before
OL,9,Fthe fatal incident happened.
OL,11,FAn inquest into their deaths found the
OL,12,Fdriver of the car had been going too
OL,13,Ffast around a bend, causing the
OL,14,Fvehicle to come off the road.
OL,16,FCrystal said the pain of losing her
OL,17,Fson to a car crash is beyond words.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
