CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777551071
OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,F"There's not enough words in the
OL,7,Fdictionary to explain the pain, well
OL,8,Fthere aren't any words to be honest.
OL,9,FIt just literally feels like your heat
OL,10,Fhas been ripped from your chest."
OL,12,F"It's the most horrific feeling in the
OL,13,Fworld because as a mother you can
OL,14,Fusually always make everything
OL,15,Fbetter...the shock is just
OL,16,Findescribable."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
