OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777551071
OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,FCrystal shared her experience to group
OL,7,Fof young drivers during the launch of
OL,8,Fthe Arrive and Alive Project at Coleg
OL,9,FCambria in Wrexham on Wednesday, 29
OL,10,FApril.
OL,12,FThe event aimed to teach learner
OL,13,Fdrivers about how to drive responsibly
OL,14,Fto prevent car accidents involving
OL,15,Fyoung people.
OL,17,FKarl Jackson is the Assistant
OL,18,FPrincipal at Coleg Cambria, he said:
OL,19,F"young people seem to pass their test
OL,20,Fand grow a set of horns. They have got
OL,21,Fto think about what they're doing."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
