PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777551071
OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,FCrystal believes more awareness and
OL,7,Feducation is needed amongst new
OL,8,Fdrivers when it comes to staying safe
OL,9,Fand carrying passengers of a similar
OL,10,Fage.
OL,12,F"I wasn't aware that it was the
OL,13,Fbiggest killer of young people. It's
OL,14,Fnot out there enough you know... road
OL,15,Fdeath is accepted and often called an
OL,16,Faccident but it is the driver's
OL,17,Fresponsibility, so it isn't an
OL,18,Faccident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777551071
OL,3,CMum who lost son in crash warns young
OL,4,Cdrivers to stay safe behind the wheel
OL,6,F"They don't set out to kill people,
OL,7,Fbut people have the keys to a lethal
OL,8,Fweapon potentially."
OL,10,F"I never thought road death would
OL,11,Faffect our family but it has, and
OL,12,Fthat's the problem you always think
OL,13,Fit'll be somebody else."
OL,15,FSince Harvey's death, Crystal is
OL,16,Fencouraging a 'graduated driving
OL,17,Flicence' to become law for all UK
OL,18,Fdrivers aged between 17 and 19.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
